Project motivation: analyze the reviews of popular Broadway shows on TripAdvisor, looking for preferences of travelers on Broadway shows. 

Scraped ~20,000 reviews of popular Broadway musicals from tripadvisor.com by Scrapy. 
Use Text-Mining/Wordcloud in python to explore the relationship between the feedback from the audiences and the characteristics of the shows. 

Please check the blog post of this project for more details:
https://nycdatascience.com/blog/student-works/a-travellers-guide-to-broadway-musicals-from-travellers-perspective/
